3
00:01:04,626 --> 00:01:06,920
<i># If we have failed in etiquette</i>

4
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:08,755
<i># Towards a man of rank so high</i>

5
00:01:09,005 --> 00:01:10,924
<i># We shall know better by and by</i>

6
