- I'm afraid not, sir.

1412
01:36:30,018 --> 01:36:31,936
Why not?

1413
01:36:32,186 --> 01:36:34,939
One cannot produce
the required vocal vigour...

1414
01:36:35,189 --> 01:36:37,984
...without the necessary
diaphragmatical support...

1415
01:36:38,234 --> 01:36:40,069
