1818
01:59:31,941 --> 01:59:34,110
# On a cloth untrue

1819
01:59:34,360 --> 01:59:36,321
# With a twisted cue

1820
01:59:36,571 --> 01:59:43,661
# And elliptical billiard balls

1821
